
{help ciw_iteropts:English Version}
{hline}
{* *! version 1.0.0  27feb2019}{...}
{syntab:迭代}
{synopt: {opt init(#)}}样本大小的初始值；默认使用闭合形式的正态近似{p_end}
{synopt: {opt iter:ate(#)}}最大迭代次数；默认值是 {cmd:iterate(500)}{p_end}
{synopt: {opt tol:erance(#)}}参数公差；默认值是 {cmd:tolerance(1e-12)}{p_end}
{synopt: {opt ftol:erance(#)}}函数公差；默认值是 {cmd:ftolerance(1e-12)}{p_end}
{synopt: [{cmd:no}]{opt log}}抑制或显示迭代日志{p_end}
{synopt: [{cmd:no}]{opt dots}}抑制或显示为点的迭代{p_end}

{synopt: {opt noti:tle}}抑制标题{p_end}